						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Hermit crabs live on land or in the ocean. Ocean dwelling hermit crabs are found in almost all oceans. Land hermit crabs live in subtropical and tropical areas of western Caribbean, the western Atlantic, the eastern Pacific, and Indo-Pacific region. Land hermit crabs live close to the shoreline and must have access to land and water.
						</text>
